text: Vincent Karchi Fong (born October 24, 1979) is an American politician who has been the U.S. representative for California's 20th congressional district from 2024. Fong was born on October 24, 1979, in Bakersfield, California to Chinese immigrants. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from California Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
